snippet.title: Amber Skye Negombo by Prime Lands Group
snippet.description:
The Launch of Amber Skye Negombo was held in line with the COVID-19 guidelines on 17th of July 2021 with the valuable customers of Prime Group.

Reserve your apartment today and enjoy the golden sunsets of Negombo and the precious investment opportunity. 

Call for more details - 0704 000 111

Experience the amazing facilities & amenities to make your life luxurious.
